quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  38,15,"ЖҒee habbaaki, si wanaa haacaango gooto, ngo alaa ruttorde"
  38,16,"ЖҒe wi': \"Joomi amen, yaccinan men geЙ“al lepte amen, ado Г‘alaande hasboore nden"
  38,17,"MuГұГұo e kon ko Й“e wi'ata; annditaa jeyaaЙ—o Amen on, Daawuuda, jom doole. Ko o Й—uuЙ—unooЙ—o tuubugol"
  38,18,"Men eltii pelle Й—en, hiЙ—e subbunhinoda e makko, ka kiikiiЙ—e e ka weetugol"
  38,19,"e colli Й—in, hiЙ—i mooЙ“indiraa, kala e majji no tuubana Mo"
  38,20,"Men semmbini laamu makko ngun, Men yeЙ—i mo Annabaaku e fasinteegal"
  38,21,"Hara kumpital wenjunooЙ“e Й“en arii maa, nde Й“e Жҙawunoo ka ganngunal"
  38,22,"Nde Й“e naatuoo ka Daawuuda, o Й—enЖҙii Й“e. ЖҒe wi'i: \"Wata a hulu ! Ko wennjuЙ“e Й—iЙ—o; goЙ—Й—o e amen tooГұii oya. Г‘aawir goonga hakkunde amen, wata a tooГұu, tinndinaa men e laawol focciingol ngol"
  38,23,"Oo ko musiЙ—Й—o am: himo jogii baali cappanЙ—e jeenay e jeenay, min miЙ—o jogii baalii gootii. O wi'i: \"Henndinam ngii\"; o foolimi e yewtere"
  38,24,"O maaki: \"Pellet, o tooГұirii ma lamndagol baalii maa ngii, waЙ—tugol e baali makko Й—in\". ЖҠuuЙ—ii ko hawtuЙ“e tooГұindirta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, si wanaa Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e, Й“e golli moЖҙЖҙuЙ—i - Й“en non no fanЙ—i. - Daawuuda felliti, wonnde Men jarribike mo. O insinanii Joomi makko, o suuyiri sujjugol, o tuubi"
  38,25,"Men yaafanii mo Й—um. Pellet non, hino woodani mo ko Amen, Й“adal e moЖҙЖҙude ruttorde"
  38,26,"Ko an yo Daawuuda, Men waЙ—ii ma lomto ka leydi. Г‘aawir goonga hakkunde yimЙ“e Й“en, wata a jokku mbeleeЙ—e, sakko Й—e majjine e laawol Allah ngol\". Pellet, Й“en majjooЙ“e e laawol Allah ngol, hino woodani Й“e lepte tiiЙ—uЙ—e, sabu ko Й“e yejjitiri kon, Г‘alaande hasboore nden"